{"title":"献给孩子的歌","authors":["张俊以"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":5,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给孩子的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张俊以"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的喇叭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵牛花向上爬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬到高高的树上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它要吹喇叭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鸟当上了主持人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即兴演讲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叽叽喳喳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大树下的孩子也跟着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱啊跳啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵牛花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在向上爬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬到月亮上面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给孩子们播放一段"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的童话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小草是大地的耳朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小草是大地的耳朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴着大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你都听到了什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地妈妈告诉他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的草都挽起手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大风就吹不走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴雨就冲不走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是每一棵小草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都把自己的身影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留给了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很美很美的山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追赶太阳的微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鸟把微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂在柳枝的嘴角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳枝让微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬上小鸟的眉梢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微笑微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微笑在大森林里奔跑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过山岗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳过林涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去追赶远方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳的微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大白鹅，小青蛙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是天才歌唱家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支小河歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河笑哈哈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支小树歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小树打伞啦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从早唱到晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快去歇歇吧！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}